---
const BOARD_REPOSITORY_URL = "https://github.com/guseoh/Board";

interface Props {
  relatedHref: string;
}

const { relatedHref } = Astro.props as Props;
---

<section class="home-section featured-project-section" aria-label="Featured project">
  <div class="home-section__head">
    <h2 class="home-section__title">현재 집중 프로젝트</h2>
    <p class="home-section__description">Java/Spring 백엔드 역량을 실제 개선 기록으로 쌓아가는 프로젝트입니다.</p>
  </div>

  <article class="project-card">
    <div class="project-card__body">
      <p class="project-card__eyebrow">Featured Project</p>
      <h3>Board</h3>
      <p>
        Spring Boot 기반 게시판 프로젝트입니다. 회원, 게시글, 댓글, OAuth2 로그인,
        QueryDSL 검색, Docker 배포, 성능 측정과 모니터링 개선 과정을 기록합니다.
      </p>

      <div class="project-tech-list" aria-label="Board project technologies">
        <span>Spring Boot</span>
        <span>JPA</span>
        <span>QueryDSL</span>
        <span>Docker</span>
        <span>CI/CD</span>
        <span>Monitoring</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card__actions">
      <a href={BOARD_REPOSITORY_URL} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub 보기</a>
      <a href={relatedHref}>관련 글 보기</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
